    "is_free": false,
    "description": "智能工厂大亨是一款管理机器人经营梦想工厂的大亨游戏。设计你的梦工厂，规划生产的每一步，研究新技术，成为大亨！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/32c3bc6efe1736ef0e0e2bd9e4593ba6.poster.avif?t=1771060972\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/32c3bc6efe1736ef0e0e2bd9e4593ba6.webm?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/32c3bc6efe1736ef0e0e2bd9e4593ba6.mp4?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>机器和机器人</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>购买新的机器和解锁更先进的机器，生产市场上的各种产品。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>购买不同颜色的新机器人，看着它们通过不同的交通工具来到你的工厂：气球、矿车、船、降落伞、PWC或巴士</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>使用技能点来提升你的机器人等级（移动速度、处理速度、充电能力、油耗）。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>为你的机器人房间购买充电器、超级充电器、无线充电器和加油机</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>升级你的机器、太阳能电池板、风力涡轮机、充电器和润滑器，以加快生产，提高效率。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/122986fd1e4bd3610a7718f22c30b2de.poster.avif?t=1771060972\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/122986fd1e4bd3610a7718f22c30b2de.webm?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/122986fd1e4bd3610a7718f22c30b2de.mp4?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>生产与市场</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>安排生产步骤</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>购买高质量的原材料以生产健康耐用的产品</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>分析市场，看透产品变化趋势</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>检查市场类别（基本-中级-高级）和特殊订单</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>提高你的健康、耐用和可持续发展等级，才能有资格拿下稀有订单。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/ed2324de73632ea2312551f447b0a343.poster.avif?t=1771060972\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/ed2324de73632ea2312551f447b0a343.webm?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/ed2324de73632ea2312551f447b0a343.mp4?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>可持续发展与经济</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>购买风力涡轮机和太阳能电池板，以减少电力成本并提高你的环保可持续性</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在你的花园里种树，成为一个可持续发展的工厂</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>赚取更多的钱和XP，在排行榜上取得第一的位置</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>精打细算，注意你的开支!不要破产!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/b3f04379a954d4174e5c5486dbfb597c.poster.avif?t=1771060972\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/b3f04379a954d4174e5c5486dbfb597c.webm?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/b3f04379a954d4174e5c5486dbfb597c.mp4?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>投资、研究与开发</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>研究新技术以改善你的工厂</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>购买新的建筑，通过铁路、海运和空运运送你的产品</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>为机器人和车间建造新的房间</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>布置你的产品区，并定义其类型为半成品和成品。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>达成阶段目标，以获得更多的XP并提升你的工厂等级。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/49f70b692ba27234997ed95977282e71.poster.avif?t=1771060972\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/49f70b692ba27234997ed95977282e71.webm?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755300/extras/49f70b692ba27234997ed95977282e71.mp4?t=1771060972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
